    "desc": "GeekxGirls.com, featuring geeky cosplay, fan art, comics, memes & more!  Fansite for lovers of sci-fi, fantasy, games, anime, comic books and all things geek.",
    "text": "  Home Photoshoots Cool Stuff Geeks Submit\n\n\n\nLinks\nGeeks are Sexy SuperHeroStuff\nNerd Approved Urban Collector\nRedbubble Sideshow Collectibles\nGeekTyrant HBO Shop\nNeatorama Tshirtbordello\nNeatoShop teeVillain\nThinkGeek Once Upon a Tee\nEntertainment Earth  TeePublic\nHeavy Metal 80's Tees\nScreen Rant Etsy\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n\nSnow White Latex Cosplay\n \n\nRuby Alexia looks gorgeous modeling this sexy and sleek Latex Snow White Set by Kitalyst! Darkslide Photography shot these lovely photos...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 18 2021\n\n\nCardi B and Megan Thee Stallion in WAP Cosplay\n \n\nCC the Geek and Tranquil Ashes look stunning cosplaying as Cardi B and Megan Thee Stallion from the music video for WAP! SF Design shot these fabulous photos...\n\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 18 2021\n\n\nScáthach from Fate/Grand Order Cosplay\n \n\nMissy Across looks fantastic cosplaying as Scáthach from Fate/Grand Order in these photo shot by Amiephotos...\n\n\"I am a being who has parted ways with death. Though I have materialized as a Servant, I am not really a Heroic Spirit, neither am I a Divine Spirit. I have lost the opportunity to die, and for that reason I am not of the living nor the dead.\"\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 16 2021\n\n\nAriel from The Little Mermaid Bathtub Cosplay\n \n\nLadykatbat look wonderful cosplaying as Ariel from The Little Mermaid and here's what she had to say...\n\n\"I got the concept to shoot a mermaid in a bathtub in my head a while back and just new I had to shoot Ariel in one. Maneuvering the in tail was difficult in a bathtub and posing was challenging but I was super happy with how this shoot turned out and how the photographer brought my vision to life.\"\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 16 2021\n\n\nKorra from The Legend of Korra Cosplay\n \n\nTranquil Ashes looks fantastic cosplaying as Korra from The Legend of Korra in these photos shot by CC the Geek...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 15 2021\n\n\nGarnet Til Alexandros & Kuja from Final Fantasy IX Cosplay\n \n\nAzumi あずみ and Luciel_Cosplayer look wonderful cosplaying together as Garnet Til Alexandros and Kuja from Final Fantasy IX in these photos shot by Rubén Ortiz Fotografía...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 15 2021\n\n\nQueen Amidala from Star Wars Cosplay\n \n\nMeg Turney looks fantastic cosplaying as Queen Amidala from Star Wars: The Phantom Menace (Episode I)...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 14 2021\n\n\nRei Ayanami from Neon Genesis Evangelion Cosplay\n \n\nJuliette Porcelain looks stunning cosplaying as Rei Ayanami from Neon Genesis Evangelion! Here's what photographer Arturo Vega, Vega CosPhoto had to say...\n\n\"Shinji didn't get on the robot, again. Time for another Rei clone to take over. Juliette Porcelain shows us the process, from when she leaves the Dummy Tank, until she gets dressed and is ready again to pilot the Eva. Hope you like what we tried to show in these photos. Greetings from Mexico!\"\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 14 2021\n\n\nTeam Rocket from Pokemon Latex Lingerie\n \n\nCandy Valentina looks stunning modelling this sexy Latex Pokemon Team Rocket Inspired Lingerie by Kitalyst! Photographer K-Maggzy shot these lovely photos...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 13 2021\n\n\nNezuko Kamado from Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Cosplay\n \n\nLady Integra from Cosplay-group Cosmo looks fabulous cosplaying as Nezuko Kamado from Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba in these photos shot by Igor Ivko...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 12 2021\n\n\nPowerline from A Goofy Movie Cosplay\n \n\nRoquois look fabulous cosplaying as Powerline from A Goofy Movie in these photos shot by SF Design...\n\n\nMore...\n\n\nJuly 12 2021\n\n\nOlder Posts\nGeekxGirls.com\nEMAIL: thegeeks@geekxgirls.com.",
